VALUES
	(1,1,'2014-09-22 16:01:23','2014-09-22 16:01:23','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2014-09-22 16:01:23','2014-09-22 16:01:23','',0,'http://southern.local/?p=1',0,'post','',1),
	(2,1,'2014-09-22 16:01:23','2014-09-22 16:01:23','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://southern.local/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','trash','open','open','','sample-page','','','2014-09-22 17:58:58','2014-09-22 17:58:58','',0,'http://southern.local/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),
	(3,1,'2014-09-22 16:14:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2014-09-22 16:14:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://southern.local/?p=3',0,'post','',0),
	(4,1,'2014-09-22 17:58:58','2014-09-22 17:58:58','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://southern.local/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 17:58:58','2014-09-22 17:58:58','',2,'http://southern.local/?p=4',0,'revision','',0),
	(5,1,'2014-09-22 17:59:09','2014-09-22 17:59:09','<strong>Rental Fee $450 Includes:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Standard set up of venue for seating up to 80.</li>\r\n	<li>All linens, table wares*, tables, chairs, and use of onsite technology\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Table wares and serving pieces are only included in this price if on site caterer handles the food and beverage for your event</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>*White or Black Table Cloths, White or Black Napkins, Plates, Assorted Glassware, Silverware</em>\r\n\r\nFood and Beverage available from <strong><a href=\"%20https://www.facebook.com/pages/Table-of-Plenty/136407276442084\" target=\"_blank\">Table of Plenty</a></strong>. Please call <a href=\"http://tel:+6623243021\" target=\"_blank\">662-324-3021</a>  for catering pricing to fit your budget.\r\n\r\nTo finalize confirmation ½ down on the total of rental fees must be delivered to The Southern to reserve the space. This is a nonrefundable amount if your event is cancelled less than 60 days prior to reservations. The remainder of your fee is due 2 weeks prior to your event. If booking an event less than 60 days in advance the total amount is due at the time of rental, this fee is non-refundable.\r\n\r\n<small class=\"subText\">We accept Visa, MasterCard, discover American Express, checks and cash.</small>','Pricing','','publish','open','open','','pricing','','','2014-09-23 20:37:43','2014-09-23 20:37:43','',0,'http://southern.local/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),
	(6,1,'2014-09-22 17:59:09','2014-09-22 17:59:09','','Pricing','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 17:59:09','2014-09-22 17:59:09','',5,'http://southern.local/?p=6',0,'revision','',0),
	(7,1,'2014-09-22 18:01:42','2014-09-22 18:01:42','Our venue can seat approximately 80 people making it perfect for your next:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wedding Reception</li>\r\n	<li>Private Business Meeting</li>\r\n	<li>Bridesmaid Luncheon</li>\r\n	<li>Private Birthday Party</li>\r\n	<li>Garden Club Meeting</li>\r\n	<li>Private Lunch or Dinner</li>\r\n	<li>Holiday Parties</li>\r\n	<li>Super Clubs</li>\r\n	<li>Baby Shower</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSome of the many benefits of using The Southern for your next event include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Caterer on site</li>\r\n	<li>All tables, chairs &amp; linens are included in rental rate</li>\r\n	<li>All china, crystal, serving pieces, and silverware included with use of onsite caterer.</li>\r\n	<li>70” Flat Screen TV downstairs</li>\r\n	<li>60” Flat Screen TV upstairs</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi</li>\r\n	<li>Surround sound system</li>\r\n	<li>Outdoor Seating available on balcony</li>\r\n	<li>Full control of the venue and atmosphere you create for your guests</li>\r\n</ul>','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2014-09-23 20:37:13','2014-09-23 20:37:13','',0,'http://southern.local/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),
	(8,1,'2014-09-22 18:01:42','2014-09-22 18:01:42','','About ','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2014-09-22 18:01:42','2014-09-22 18:01:42','',7,'http://southern.local/?p=8',0,'revision','',0),
	(9,1,'2014-09-22 18:02:33','2014-09-22 18:02:33','<span style=\"color: #666666;\">[dopbs]</span><span style=\"color: #acacac;\">.</span>\r\n\r\nOk I am going to need you to find what you think the best solution is for the calendar needs I am going to list below….just send me pricing…let’s go ahead and pay for the calendar to get all the bells and whistles so it is easier than making changes after the fact with Cartney Hunt unless you totally disagree with me!\r\nThere will be three day parts someone can use the space for:  Morning 6-10am, Midday 10-2, and Evening 4-until\r\nShe does not want the customer to be able to reserve from this only to be able to do this on the backend of the website to show the venue as booked for people needing that information\r\nI would make sure contact information is prominent on this screen...\r\n\r\nProminent Contact Info here!\r\nSome setup of the venue space may occur after entering the venue space.  Please alert the staff you book your appointment with of the exact start time of your event.','Availability','','publish','open','open','','availability','','','2014-09-23 21:30:47','2014-09-23 21:30:47','',0,'http://southern.local/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),
