	(19,1,'2014-09-22 19:12:07','2014-09-22 19:12:07','Let us take the stress out of planning your next event. Our unique, social venue in the heart of beautiful, Downtown Columbus provides you with all the linens, table wares, and an on-site caterer making planning a breeze. No trips to multiple sites to secure the items you need for your event, just let our experienced staff handle all the details as you prepare to enjoy your event.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Southern includes beautiful views from our balcony overlooking Main Street, reclaimed pine wood floors from the turn of the century all beautifully combined with the modern technology you may need for your business presentations. The intimate and private atmosphere of The Southern allows you and your guests to gather and enjoy each other and for you to control the atmosphere and privacy of having an event in a closed location. Enjoy our full service venue for all your social needs!</p>\r\n[calendarModule]We are now booking for 2014[/calendarModule]\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><button class=\"blueButton\"><a title=\"Availability\" href=\"http://southern.local/availability/\">BOOK YOUR RESERVATION TODAY</a></button></p>\r\n\r\n</div>','Welcome','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2014-09-23 17:54:06','2014-09-23 17:54:06','',0,'http://southern.local/?page_id=19',0,'page','',0),
