	(44,1,'2014-09-23 19:50:00','2014-09-23 19:50:00','<strong>Rental Fee $450 Includes:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Standard set up of venue for seating up to 80.</li>\n	<li>All linens, table wares*, tables, chairs, and use of onsite technology\n<ul>\n	<li>Table wares and serving pieces are only included in this price if on site caterer handles the food and beverage for your event</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<em>*White or Black Table Cloths, White or Black Napkins, Plates, Assorted Glassware, Silverware</em>\n\nFood and Beverage available from <strong><a href=\"%20https://www.facebook.com/pages/Table-of-Plenty/136407276442084\" target=\"_blank\">Table of Plenty</a></strong>. Please call <a href=\"http://tel:+6623243021\" target=\"_blank\">662-324-3021</a>  for catering pricing to fit your budget.\n\nTo finalize confirmation ½ down on the total of rental fees must be delivered to The Southern to reserve the space. This is a nonrefundable amount if your event is cancelled less than 60 days prior to reservations. The remainder of your fee is due 2 weeks prior to your event. If booking an event less than 60 days in advance the total amount is due at the time of rental, this fee is non-refundable.\n\nWe accept Visa, MasterCard, discover American Express, checks and cash.','Pricing','','inherit','open','open','','5-autosave-v1','','','2014-09-23 19:50:00','2014-09-23 19:50:00','',5,'http://southern.local/5-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(45,1,'2014-09-23 18:35:40','2014-09-23 18:35:40','• Rental Fee $450 Includes:\r\n\r\nStandard set up of venue for seating up to 80.\r\n\r\nAll linens, table wares*, tables, chairs, and use of onsite technology\r\n\r\nTable wares and serving pieces are only included in this price if on site caterer handles the food and beverage for your event\r\n\r\n*White or Black Table Cloths, White or Black Napkins, Plates, Assorted Glassware, Silverware\r\n\r\nFood and Beverage available from Table of Plenty (make clickable to this link: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Table-of-Plenty/136407276442084 ) Please call 662-324-3021 (can we make that a clickable link from a cell phone view of the page?) for catering pricing to fit your budget.\r\n\r\nTo finalize confirmation ½ down on the total of rental fees must be delivered to The Southern to reserve the space. This is a nonrefundable amount if your event is cancelled less than 60 days prior to reservations. The remainder of your fee is due 2 weeks prior to your event. If booking an event less than 60 days in advance the total amount is due at the time of rental, this fee is non-refundable.\r\n\r\nWe should also note somewhere on this screen that they accept Visa, MasterCard, discover American Express, checks and cash as payment forms…Please place this small somewhere on the page as a sub text item.','Pricing','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2014-09-23 18:35:40','2014-09-23 18:35:40','',5,'http://southern.local/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
